			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Colony Tadpoling Centre (ReCon command \"oe tc_teleport\")\r\n- Interact with the mind flayer device that controls the pods, and choose to release the occupants of the pods.\r\n- Zevlor will play this AD on his first combat turn in the resulting combat."
				},
